[
    {
        "start": 0.0,
        "end": 1.74,
        "text": "People who are struggling to lose weight,",
        "pause_after": false,
        "tonal_change": false
    },
    {
        "start": 2.12,
        "end": 4.12,
        "text": "they usually know the theoretical stuff,",
        "pause_after": false,
        "tonal_change": false
    },
    {
        "start": 4.18,
        "end": 6.52,
        "text": "but they're not able to beat their own cravings.",
        "pause_after": false,
        "tonal_change": false
    },
    {
        "start": 6.54,
        "end": 8.62,
        "text": "I worked with someone who couldn't stop eating,",
        "pause_after": false,
        "tonal_change": false
    },
    {
        "start": 8.62,
        "end": 10.86,
        "text": "was extremely overweight, very unhappy.",
        "pause_after": false,
        "tonal_change": false
    },
    {
        "start": 11.2,
        "end": 12.84,
        "text": "And you remember being a premature baby,",
        "pause_after": false,
        "tonal_change": false
    },
    {
        "start": 12.9,
        "end": 14.74,
        "text": "almost died because he was so little.",
        "pause_after": false,
        "tonal_change": false
    },
    {
        "start": 14.9,
        "end": 16.4,
        "text": "Every time the mother fed him and he brought out the milk,",
        "pause_after": false,
        "tonal_change": false
    },
    {
        "start": 16.4,
        "end": 18.94,
        "text": "she would cry hysterically and get really upset",
        "pause_after": false,
        "tonal_change": false
    },
    {
        "start": 18.94,
        "end": 19.74,
        "text": "because he was going to die.",
        "pause_after": false,
        "tonal_change": false
    },
    {
        "start": 19.74,
        "end": 21.24,
        "text": "But when he began to keep the milk in,",
        "pause_after": false,
        "tonal_change": false
    },
    {
        "start": 21.3,
        "end": 22.64,
        "text": "she went, oh, he's such a good eater.",
        "pause_after": false,
        "tonal_change": false
    },
    {
        "start": 22.74,
        "end": 25.38,
        "text": "Look, he's getting so fat and it's all lovely.",
        "pause_after": false,
        "tonal_change": false
    },
    {
        "start": 25.62,
        "end": 27.48,
        "text": "So his mind had an interesting belief.",
        "pause_after": false,
        "tonal_change": false
    },
    {
        "start": 27.66,
        "end": 29.78,
        "text": "If I don't eat, it upsets people.",
        "pause_after": false,
        "tonal_change": false
    },
    {
        "start": 29.78,
        "end": 32.86,
        "text": "So I'm eating to get that feeling of happiness,",
        "pause_after": false,
        "tonal_change": false
    },
    {
        "start": 33.08,
        "end": 34.6,
        "text": "but you now have got to change it.",
        "pause_after": false,
        "tonal_change": false
    },
    {
        "start": 34.66,
        "end": 36.86,
        "text": "Now we have to give them a new message",
        "pause_after": false,
        "tonal_change": false
    },
    {
        "start": 36.86,
        "end": 38.94,
        "text": "to start to say that you love leaving food.",
        "pause_after": false,
        "tonal_change": false
    },
    {
        "start": 39.1,
        "end": 40.84,
        "text": "You actually are much more of a fruit person",
        "pause_after": false,
        "tonal_change": false
    },
    {
        "start": 40.84,
        "end": 41.98,
        "text": "than an ice cream person.",
        "pause_after": false,
        "tonal_change": false
    },
    {
        "start": 42.2,
        "end": 43.64,
        "text": "You don't really like all that junk.",
        "pause_after": false,
        "tonal_change": false
    },
    {
        "start": 43.74,
        "end": 46.26,
        "text": "You like real, healthy, nourishing food.",
        "pause_after": false,
        "tonal_change": false
    }
]